A preview segment for NBC's Nightly News turned into a sweet father-son encounter when anchor Lester Holt met his own son on-air.

Stefan Holt, who has followed in his father's footsteps and anchors the local news in Chicago, said 'Hi, Dad!' before handing over to the national host for a preview of that evening's stories.

Lester responded 'proud of you' before going on to walk viewers through what was coming up later that evening.

